column5: I was stopped and searched both ways....going into Canada and coming back into the USA.And.....I didn't mind it a bit.VERY professional on both sides of the border.
I had the same experiance this year. Very professional, no search but they did ask to look at a few things. No problems.
As long as you don't hear the snapping of latex behind you it's OK....
No problems bringing back suitcases full of cash from VS, eh? Hahaha, HRG
No problem there.....It was a small suitcase in the trunk
For all you have done to start and keep this site going, I hope the small case was full of Large Bills!!
